---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BreadcrumbSchema from '../components/schema/BreadcrumbSchema.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Underdial terms of service — eligibility, subscriptions, affiliate disclosure, advice disclaimer, and limitation of liability."
  path="/terms"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <BreadcrumbSchema crumbs={[{ name: 'Terms of Service', url: `${SITE.url}/terms` }]} />
  </Fragment>

  <p class="brand">{SITE.name}</p>
  <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="effective">Effective Date: June 14, 2026</p>

  <p>
    These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of Underdial ("the app")
    and the website at <a href={SITE.url}>{SITE.url}</a>. By using the app or the
    website, you agree to these Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
  <p>
    You must be at least 13 years of age to use Underdial. By using the app, you
    represent that you meet this age requirement.
  </p>

  <h2>2. No Account Required</h2>
  <p>
    Underdial has no sign-in and no user accounts. Your box, wrist settings, and
    check history are stored locally on your device. You are responsible for
    safeguarding your device and any backups you choose to keep.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Subscriptions</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Underdial Plus</strong> is an optional auto-renewing subscription.
    Subscriptions are managed by Apple through the App Store. Key terms:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pricing is shown in-app at the time of purchase, in your local currency.</li>
    <li>Payment is charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase.</li>
    <li>Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.</li>
    <li>You can manage subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal in <strong>Settings &rarr; Apple ID &rarr; Subscriptions</strong> on your iPhone.</li>
    <li>Refund requests must be made through Apple. We cannot process refunds directly.</li>
    <li>Price changes take effect at the next renewal and require notice and consent where required by Apple.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Free vs Plus</h2>
  <p>
    The free app gives you two full watch checks plus unlimited browsing and
    collection tracking. Underdial Plus unlocks unlimited checks, the
    cheaper-alternatives list on every result, the full Box Audit, and the
    reasoning behind each verdict. Current pricing and the up-to-date list of
    what each tier includes are shown in-app at the time of purchase and may
    evolve as new features ship. Continued use of an active subscription after a
    feature change constitutes acceptance of the updated tier definition.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Affiliate Links and Retailer Disclosure</h2>
  <p>
    Watch detail pages and selected articles may include
    <strong>&ldquo;Buy from&rdquo;</strong> links to third-party retailers. These
    are affiliate links delivered through the Awin network: when you click one and
    complete a purchase, we may earn a small commission from the retailer.
    <strong>This does not affect the price you pay.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Affiliate links are clearly disclosed on every buy screen. Underdial is not a
    retailer and does not sell, distribute, or ship watches. Your purchase
    contract is with the retailer, and any questions about pricing, shipping,
    returns, warranty, or product authenticity must be directed to them.
  </p>
  <p>
    This disclosure is provided in accordance with the FTC's
    <em>Guides Concerning the Use of Endorsements and Testimonials in Advertising</em>.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Advice and Recommendations</h2>
  <p>
    Verdicts, redundancy flags, cheaper-alternative lists, and Box Audit
    insights are best-effort guidance based on catalog data and the parameters
    you provide (budget, wrist size, and the watches in your box). They are not
    professional, financial, or investment advice. Watches are a personal and
    sometimes subjective purchase &mdash; treat Underdial as a second opinion,
    not the final word, and confirm specifications and fit with the retailer
    before you buy.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Acceptable Use</h2>
  <p>
    No abuse, scraping, reverse-engineering, or interference with the service.
    We may restrict access for conduct that violates these Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
  <p>
    The Underdial name, logo, design, and code are our property. Watch brand
    names, model names, reference numbers, and product imagery are the property
    of their respective owners and are used for informational and identification
    purposes only.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
  <p>
    Underdial is provided "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" without warranties of any
    kind, express or implied. Catalog specifications, pricing, and availability
    are general reference and may not reflect every variant, region, or change
    by the manufacturer or retailer. We make no claims about the condition,
    authenticity, or suitability of any watch sold by a third-party retailer.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the maximum extent permitted by law, our total liability for any claim
    related to the app or the website shall not exceed the amount you paid to us
    in the prior twelve months. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental,
    special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from or related to your
    use of the service, including loss of data or a purchasing decision you made
    using the app.
  </p>

  <h2>11. Deleting Your Data</h2>
  <p>
    Because there is no account, your data lives on your device. Use the in-app
    reset (Settings &rarr; Reset Data) or delete the app to remove it. This
    cannot be undone. Removing the app does not automatically cancel an active
    App Store subscription &mdash; manage subscriptions in
    <strong>Settings &rarr; Apple ID &rarr; Subscriptions</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
  <p>
    We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be
    communicated through the app. Continued use after changes constitutes
    acceptance of the revised Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>13. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For questions about these Terms, contact us at:
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.supportEmail}`}>{SITE.supportEmail}</a>
  </p>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
